0.7
  * freetype kerning fix;
  * schrift kerning fix;
  * -noautoload/-noautosave parameters;
  * mp updates;
  * october: fixes;
  * del key (input edit);
  * fix in reset layout (change font size on the fly);
  * /stop command in autoscript.

0.6
  * urzi English translation;
  * new game: october;
  * better settings loading;
  * updated parser module;
  * Android: compat with rotate lock;
  * fix in paging.

0.5
  * tts support for: Linux, Windows and Android.
  * !tts command;
  * Accessibility friendly Android version;
  * better support for Android soft-keyboards;
  * bugfixes.

0.4
  * space distance while font resizing fix;
  * freetype support (make WITH_TRUETYPE=1);
  * libschrift support (make WITH_SCHRIFT=1).
  * / -> ! in system wide commands;
  * !saves - list saves;
  * !rm - remove save;
  * fix scroll on title screen.

0.3
  * mp 2.2.2;
  * parser correct messages fix;
  * autoscript cr/lf compat;
  * conf.directory can be { };
  * conf.width (maximum width in elements);
  * -d as -debug;
  * more clever resize -> scroll;
  * bug fixes.

0.2
  * ctrl+/ctrl- - changes font size;
  * -i <autoscript> feature;
  * conf.scroll_drag support;
  * Android port;
  * use SDL2 Render API (faster);
  * conf.settings feature;
  * metaparser + games fixes;
  * bugfixes.

0.1
  * Initial release
